# Mobile (Expo)

- Expo Router v4 file-based routes under `apps/mobile/app/`
- NativeWind v4 for styling
- @rnmapbox/maps for the map layer
- Prefer shared types from monorepo packages; keep screen files thin

## Screens

| Route | Role |
|-------|------|
| `(tabs)/map` | Memory map (main) |
| `(tabs)/discover` | Discovery mode |
| `(tabs)/live` | Live map |
| `(tabs)/profile` | Profile + chapters |
| `create-pin` | New memory |
| `pin/[id]`, `chapter/[id]` | Detail views |
